m the spec folder and relevant implementation files. If no active findings for an angle, record clean surfaces and ruled-out checks honestly.\n3. `phase_synthesis`: produce resource-map and review-report under artifact_dir only. The report must preserve strongest active verdict from findings.\n4. Verify with read/list checks before returning the final sentinel.\n\nFinal response requirement: after successful verification, output exactly:\nFANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:glm","subagent_type":"general","task_id":"","command":"/deep:review fanout-lineage"},"output":"<task id=\"ses_0e878236bffetcQ8G1WHcmajk7\" state=\"completed\">\n<task_result>\nThe `deep-review` task tool call completed with an error and wrote no files.\n\nIt refused on its own LEAF boundary:\n\n`Failed gate: ILLEGAL NESTING / LEAF-only boundary`\n\nReason returned by the agent: it interpreted the requested Task dispatch as forbidden nesting and also said the `deep-review` agent may execute only one review iteration, not the full 50-iteration lineage.\n</task_result>\n</task>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_0e87c1454ffeG34NiBsfe1bGX1","sessionId":"ses_0e878236bffetcQ8G1WHcmajk7","model":{"modelID":"gpt-5.5-fast","providerID":"openai"},"truncated":false},"title":"Run GLM review lineage","time":{"start":1782806207638,"end":1782806381276}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_08021b422c2a6211016a437677b2648191a98d3580c71422b6"}},"id":"prt_f1786c3ab001k2qKMjHLayVy2c","sessionID":"ses_0e87c1454ffeG34NiBsfe1bGX1","messageID":"msg_f17865d0b001A2GwX5i7w7IE62"}}
